  "summary": {
    "en": "A 168-piece Luminous Explorer glow set with rotating balls, blue standard rods, glow rods, clips, rings, storage bag, and flag.",
    "zh": "168件 Luminous Explorer 夜光套装，含旋转球、蓝色标准杆、夜光杆、夹子、套圈、收纳袋和旗子。"
  },
  "description": {
    "en": [
      "The 168-piece LONDY Luminous Explorer set uses blue rotating balls, blue standard rods, and glow rods for night-theme structures.",
      "The set includes 50 rotating balls, 70 blue standard support rods, 16 short glow rods, 14 long glow rods, clips, rings, storage bag, and flag.",
      "The blue space-themed color box is marked ages 5+ and highlights glow-in-the-dark building play.",
      "Set total is RMB 187.67, shown as about $28.87."
    ],
    "zh": [
      "168件 LONDY Luminous Explorer 采用蓝色旋转球、蓝色标准杆和夜光杆，适合搭建夜光主题结构。",
      "套装包含50个旋转球、70根蓝色标准支撑杆、16根短夜光杆、14根长夜光杆、夹子、套圈、收纳袋和旗子。",
      "蓝色太空主题彩盒标注适用 5 岁以上，突出夜光拼搭玩法。",
      "套装合计为人民币187.67元，折算约 $28.87。"
    ]
  },
